	<<His>> hands tremble, but become more steady as <<he>> cleans your bruises and scratches. "Please, forgive me." <<His>> voice is full of guilt and shame. <<His>> focus seems to be the only thing stopping <<him>> from crying. <<pain -50>><<lllpain>>
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Run|Forest Gwylan Stalk Pain]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Sit still|Forest Gwylan Stalk Pain]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Hug Gwylan|Forest Gwylan Stalk Pain]]>><<set $phase to 3>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<gyearning>>
	<br>
	<<if displayDefiantOption(500)>>
		<<link [[Get revenge|Forest Gwylan Stalk Pain]]>><<set $phase to 4>><<stress -16>><<wolfDefiant 500>><</link>><<defianttext 500>><<lllstress>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $angel gte 6>>
		<<link [[Forgive|Forest Gwylan Stalk Pain]]>><<set $phase to 5>><<trauma -12>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 3>><</link>><<ggyearning>><<lltrauma>><<angel>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<He>> whines, and rolls off of you.
	<br><br>

	<<if $consensual is 0>>
		"You put up a fine struggle. It was thrilling. I'm sorry if I took it too far." <<He>> licks you, before helping you stand and dusting you off. "I'll see you at the shop."
	<<else>>
		"I couldn't help it. My body craved yours. I had to chase you." <<He>> helps you up, but fails to keep eye contact with you. "I'll see you at the shop."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> pauses. "Unless you'd like to walk back together?"
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Go with Gwylan|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<gyearning>>
