	<<link [[Stay here|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Forest Gwylan Stalk Pain
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is 1>>
	<<set $forest += random(-3,3)*5>><<set $forest = Math.clamp($forest, 21, 100)>>
	You don't take a chance. As soon as the pain is no longer overwhelming, you scramble away from <<him>> and refuse to look back.
	<br><br>

	You keep running. You lose your way, but you keep running.
	<br><br>

	Finally, you pause to catch your breath. You weren't followed.
	<br><br>

	<<clotheson>>
	<<endcombat>>

	<<link [[Next|Forest]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif $phase is 2>>
	You sit still, not saying anything. <<He>> continues to tend to you, until <<he>> starts gently petting your head. <<pain -10>><<llpain>>
	<br><br>

	"I won't insult you with excuses. I'll only ask for forgiveness, and if words alone aren't enough, I'll... I'll find some way to make amends. Or I'll simply leave, if that's what you prefer."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> looks like <<hes>> about to pull you into a hug, but hesitates. <<He>> gathers <<his>> supplies. You stay silent.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> stands, and helps you do the same. "Let me guide you out of the forest, at least."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Go with Gwylan|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<gyearning>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Stay here|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif $phase is 3>>
	You wrap <<him>> in a tight hug. <<He>> freezes for only a moment, before eagerly returning it. <<pain -10>><<llpain>>
	<br><br>

	"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "name">>..."
	<br><br>

	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>"It's okay. Just be more careful next time, please," you say.
		<<case "bratty">>"Just don't do that again," you say. "You're better than this."
		<<default>>"It's okay. It doesn't hurt as much anymore. Just don't do that to me again."
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> pulls away, smiling, and helps you stand. "Let me guide you out of the forest, at least."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Go with Gwylan|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<gyearning>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Stay here|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif $phase is 4>>
	<<His>> guard is down. As <<he>> turns back to you, you land a solid punch right across <<his>> face. <<He>> falls back on the ground, looking up at you with shock.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> rubs <<his>> cheek. <<He>> opens <<his>> mouth to say something, but stops <<himself>>.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Help <<him>> up|Forest Gwylan Stalk Revenge]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Leave <<him>> in the dirt|Forest Gwylan Stalk Revenge]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	You wrap <<him>> in a tight hug, and let your warmth flow over <<him>>. <<He>> freezes for only a moment, before eagerly returning it. <<pain -10>><<llpain>>
	<br><br>

	"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "name">>..."
	<br><br>

	"I forgive you," you say. "I think you just need to forgive yourself."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> holds you tighter. "You're too good for this world."
	<br><br>

	You separate. "Let me guide you out of the forest, at least."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Go with Gwylan|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<gyearning>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Stay here|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Forest Gwylan Stalk Revenge
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is 1>>
	"There, now we're even," you say. You stand and reach your hand out. "Don't ever fucking do that again."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> stares at you a moment, before giggling and taking your hand. You help <<him>> stand up, and pull <<him>> into a hug. <<He>> returns the embrace. "Thank you, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>."
	<br><br>

	You separate. "Let me guide you out of the forest, at least."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Go with Gwylan|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 1>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>><<handholdingvirginitywarning>><<gyearning>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Stay here|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	You turn and walk away from Gwylan.
	<br><br>

	"Wait," <<he>> says. <<His>> voice almost sounds desperate. "Let me walk you back to the shop, at least. Please. It's dangerous."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Go with Gwylan|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 3>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Leave|Forest Gwylan Walk Shop]]>><<set $phase to 4>><<npcincr Gwylan dom -2>><</link>><<lyearning>>
	<br>
<</if>>


:: Forest Gwylan Lure
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylan.lureDistance -= 5>>
<<if $phase is "willing">>
	<span class="lewd">You willingly follow the beautiful voice as it sings to you.</span>
<<else>>
	<<if $willpowerSuccess>>
		<<set $gwylan.lureWill++>>
		<span class="teal">You dig your heels in, and try to resist following the song.</span> <<if $gwylan.lureWill lt 4>>Your legs still carry you forward, but you're gaining control.<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<span class="red">You can't resist the beautiful song.</span> <<if $willpower lte 500>><<willpower 1>><<gwillpower>><</if>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $gwylan.lureSong is 1 and $islander_language gte 100>>
	You recognise the language. <span class="blue">It's the islander tongue.</span>
	<br><br>
<</if>>
<<gwylanSong>>
<br><br>

<<if $gwylan.lureWill gte 4>>
	<span class="green">You stop.</span>
	<br><br>

	You shake your head, pushing away the song's influence, and start running in the opposite direction.
	<br><br>
	<<set $forest to $gwylan.lureDistance + 5>>
	<<run delete $gwylan.lureWill>><<run delete $gwylan.lureDistance>>
	<<foresthuntstart "Gwylan">>
<<elseif $gwylan.lureDistance lte 0>>
	You see a small hole in the ground, just big enough to crawl through. It yawns open wider before your eyes.
	<br><br>

	<span class="red">You crawl in.</span>
	<br><br>

	<<if $islander_language gte 100>>
		<<for $_s to $gwylan.lureSong; $_s lt 6; $_s++>>
			<<gwylanSong>>
			<br><br>
		<</for>>
	<</if>>
	<<gwylanSong "end">>
	<br><br>

	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("aurigaScarConfront")>>
		Something is wrong. It's empty. Dark. This tunnel has no walls. No ceiling.
		<br><br>

		You continue crawling forward, and realise far too late that there's <span class="red">no air, either</span>. Your vision goes hazy in an instant, stars creeping into the edges as your muscles seize.
		<br><br>

		No hope. No safety. No life.
		<br><br>

		A pain overtakes your chest, spreading out from your heart. You look down, and see a <span class="tentacle">crackling scar</span> erupting from your skin in the same spot. <<pain 4>><<trauma 50>>
		<br><br>

		No glory. No pleasure. Damnation.
		<br><br>

		Something appears in the emptiness ahead. A pair of antlers, made of the same writhing nothingness as your scar. You collapse. There's no ground. You fall.
		<br><br>

		Nowhere.
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next|Forest Shop Nowhere Passout]]>><<set $forest to 0>><<endevent>><<pass 15>><<run delete $gwylan.lureSong>><<run delete $gwylan.lureDistance>><<run delete $gwylan.lureWill>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Next|Forest Gwylan Ritual Forced]]>><<set $forest to 0>><<endevent phaseless>><<run delete $gwylan.lureSong>><<run delete $gwylan.lureDistance>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<link [[Walk towards the singing|Forest Gwylan Lure]]>><<set $phase to "willing">><<stress -1>><<trauma -1>><<arousal 500>><<pass 5>><</link>><<lstress>><<ltrauma>><<garousal>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Resist|Forest Gwylan Lure]]>><<set $phase to "resist">><<pass 5>><</link>><<gwylanWillpowerDifficulty>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Forest Gwylan Ritual Forced
<<set $location to "forest_shop_garden">><<set $outside to 0>><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>

<<if $phase is "vored">>
	With a great heave, the snake pushes you up and through its gullet once more, expelling you from its body. You land on a hard stone surface and gasp for breath. Your vision is blurry.
	<br><br>

	You hear a hiss, followed by a disturbing crackling sound. You look around. You appear to be in Gwylan's garden, and there's no sign of the snake.
<<else>>
	You emerge in Gwylan's garden. A trapdoor closes behind you.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if isPregnancyEnding()>>
	<<pregnancyPassout "forestShopGarden">>
<<elseif _gwylanStatus.includes("reunion")>>
	Before you can fully get your bearings, a pair of arms wrap around you. It's Gwylan.
	<<if $phase is "vored">>
		<<He>> doesn't seem to mind how slimy you are.
	<</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
		"<<pcPetname "Gwylan">>! Where have you been?! Do you have any idea how worried I was?" <<if _gwylanTF.revealed>><<His>> tail beats on the ground.<</if>>
	<<else>>
		"I'm glad I found you. I haven't seen you in ages, I thought you were gone for good. What happened to you?"
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<gwylanReunion>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> pets your head. "Since you're here, let's make up for some lost time."
	<br><br>

	<span class="red">You don't know when <<he>> started swinging a small red pendant in front of you. It's hard to focus. Your eyelids feel heavy.</span>
	<br><br>

	<<if playerChastity()>>
		<<link [[Tell Gwylan you can't because of your chastity device|Gwylan Chastity Removal]]>><<set $phase to "forced">><</link>>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Agree to do the ritual|Gwylan Ritual Start Garden]]>><<clotheson>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "lured">><</link>>
	<</if>>
	<br>
	<<if $gwylan.lureWill gte 2 or $phase is "resist" or $phase is "vored">>
		<<link [[Resist|Forest Gwylan Ritual Resist]]>><</link>><<gwylanWillpowerDifficulty>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<hypnosisText "You can't bring yourself to resist after giving in to the song.">>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<elseif $gwylan.hunting gte 2>>
	"There you are, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>." Gwylan crouches down before you, wearing nothing but <<his>> hat and a seductive smile.
	<<if $phase is "vored">>
		"You're all slimy. Let's get you washed, then we can conduct our ritual."
	<<elseif $gwylan.lureWill gte 2 or $phase is "resist">>
		"You're a <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "naughty">>, trying to resist my call like that."
	<<else>>
		"You're such a <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "good">>, coming right to me when I call you."
	<</if>>
	<<He>> pets your head. <<trauma -1>><<ltrauma>>
	<br><br>

	"You've kept me waiting. It's okay, though. You're here now. Let's make up for that lost time."
	<br><br>

	<span class="red">You don't know when <<he>> started swinging a small red pendant in front of you. It's hard to focus. Your eyelids feel heavy.</span>
	<br><br>

	<<if playerChastity()>>
		<<link [[Tell Gwylan you can't because of your chastity device|Gwylan Chastity Removal]]>><<set $phase to "forced">><</link>>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Agree to do the ritual|Gwylan Ritual Start Garden]]>><<clotheson>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "lured">><</link>>
	<</if>>
	<br>
	<<if $gwylan.lureWill gte 2 or $phase is "resist" or $phase is "vored">>
		<<link [[Resist|Forest Gwylan Ritual Resist]]>><</link>><<gwylanWillpowerDifficulty>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<hypnosisText "You can't bring yourself to resist after giving in to the song.">>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "name">>! What a pleasant surprise!" Gwylan's smiling face greets you as <<he>> crouches down to your level. "I was calling out to the forest for the ritual. It seems my song works on you now, too!" <<He>> pets your head. <<trauma -1>><<ltrauma>>
	<br><br>

	"Since you're here... you're not busy, are you?" <<He>> smiles seductively. <span class="lewd">"I prefer your company for the ritual."</span>
	<br><br>

	<<if playerChastity()>>
		<<link [[Tell Gwylan you can't because of your chastity device|Gwylan Chastity Removal]]>><<set $phase to "forced">><</link>>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Agree to do the ritual|Gwylan Ritual Start Garden]]>><<clotheson>><<endevent>><<set $phase to "lured">><</link>>
	<</if>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Say no|Forest Gwylan Ritual No]]>><<npcincr Gwylan dom -4>><</link>><<llyearning>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<run delete $gwylan.lureWill>>

